WEBVTT

00:01.939 --> 00:05.265
With up to 1,500 kilometers on just one tank of fuel,...

00:05.455 --> 00:08.285
...the new M-Class is a real master of efficiency.

00:09.145 --> 00:10.545
Compared to its predecessor,...

00:10.662 --> 00:14.978
...the entire model range consumes an average of 25% less fuel.

00:16.253 --> 00:18.883
The third generation M-Class has been revamped.

00:19.211 --> 00:21.673
With the smallest turning circle in its market segment,...

00:21.924 --> 00:23.326
...an ultra - modern engine lineup,...

00:23.635 --> 00:25.160
...innovative assistance systems,...

00:25.244 --> 00:27.820
...as well as both on and off-road capability.

00:30.943 --> 00:34.150
The interior design concept means even more comfort.

00:34.438 --> 00:35.607
On long road trips,...

00:35.691 --> 00:40.626
...the spacious interior of the vehicle offers passengers the right comfort of a premium sedan.

00:45.437 --> 00:51.971
Further improved safety in the new M-Class is provided by the familiar assistance systems from the S and E-Class.

